469
00:22:58,960 --> 00:23:00,680
That was my idea.

470
00:23:01,160 --> 00:23:02,480
Yeah, but it’s thanks to me
that I forgot the letter in my pocket,

471
00:23:02,560 --> 00:23:04,280
so it’s actually thanks to me.

472
00:23:04,520 --> 00:23:05,680
Fine.

473
00:23:05,920 --> 00:23:07,000
What happened, girls, are you itching?

474
00:23:07,480 --> 00:23:08,800
It burns.

475
00:23:08,960 --> 00:23:10,320
Look at the letter, until when is the girl suspended from kindergarten?

476
00:23:11,480 --> 00:23:13,800
No, it just says "We request
to address this matter urgently

477
00:23:16,720 --> 00:23:18,640
and no, your child will not be able to attend kindergarten."

478
00:23:19,080 --> 00:23:20,560
Check the envelope if there’s a date or something.

479
00:23:20,640 --> 00:23:22,160
"To the parents of the girl Rotem Gabatz."

480
00:23:25,080 --> 00:23:26,040
"להורי הילדה רותם גבץ."

481
00:23:27,920 --> 00:23:30,120
What?
-The letter isn’t even for our girl.

482
00:23:31,160 --> 00:23:34,480
I’m telling you, if they go bald
it’s only because of your irresponsibility.

483
00:23:35,160 --> 00:23:36,040
Or maybe it’s in the genes.

484
00:23:39,160 --> 00:23:41,120
Let’s just say I’m more of a basketball person.

485
00:23:42,520 --> 00:23:44,000
Try to get past the knee.

486
00:23:45,200 --> 00:23:47,920
Every Saturday someone moves, moves...

487
00:23:49,000 --> 00:23:50,880
Just one more minute of the...

488
00:23:53,480 --> 00:23:56,320
Who? That guy’s son who brings the shampoo...
Sorry, the importer’s son.

489
00:23:58,880 --> 00:24:01,600
I wonder who the first nutcase is. No...

490
00:24:03,880 --> 00:24:05,640
I hope they’re making it in the loopers.

491
00:24:08,880 --> 00:24:10,040
Did you put something on them?

492
00:24:12,640 --> 00:24:14,480
I just found out, in the car.

493
00:24:16,080 --> 00:24:17,560
What’s wrong with Dad? What’s wrong with Dad?

494
00:24:19,720 --> 00:24:22,080
What were you laughing at?
-How he ran away.

495
00:24:23,240 --> 00:24:24,840
It’s funny, right?
-Sorry.

